Reasoning: The paper introduces a new paradigm of grounding and solving in Answer Set Programming (ASP) that deals with continuously changing logic programs, allowing for advanced forms of search, interaction with an environment, and state changing operations. This makes it relevant to several sub-categories of computer science, including Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Logic in Computer Science (cs.LO), Programming Languages (cs.PL), Software Engineering (cs.SE), and Robotics (cs.RO).
